memberOrga:
POLLINIS is comprised of an Association a but non lucratif in France and an ASBL in Belgium. &#xd;
&#xd;
POLLINIS defends the interests of 1.3 million European citizens who have participated in and supported our political actions and campaigns, and all European citizens who consume agricultural products and who, as taxpayers, finance the Common Agricultural Policy.&#xd;
&#xd;
POLLINIS is exclusively funded by individual donations from over 20,000 members of the public throughout Europe annually (20,087 in 2016).
